abstract: University of Tennesee-Chattanooga enters Associated Press poll at No 25; University of South Carolina remains at No 1.
lead_paragraph: Jim Foster became the first coach in women’s basketball to lead four programs to the Top 25 when Chattanooga entered the Associated Press poll at No. 25.

headline.main: Chattanooga Coach Sets an A.P. Rankings Record
